{"tid":1810771,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳梓維到底做唔做得掂","createTime":"2020-01-04T07:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T07:10:19.000Z","uid":300761,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"900e85896efe2231dbb71411be96473c061219b5","tid":1810771,"uid":300761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲記得陳梓維係邊個 冇錯 佢就係手寫政綱贏咗區議會果個素人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁其實手寫都冇野嘅 誠意滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但去到2020其他人個個開晒工 佢就連助理都未請到 唔係冇人應徵 而係佢要求太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我希望佢哋嘅學歷唔會高過我，如果唔係會自我中心。。。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬你CE 0分連毅進都肥佬 論學歷會低過你嘅人真係唔知邊到搵 俾你搵到嘅 又真係幫到你？<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係有大學生嚟應徵面試 佢話自己唔識英文 期望收到份中文CV 叫個大學生反省下自己呢到做法嘅不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係個大學生我可能會當場嚟個City反枱俾條傻仔睇下 你自己講緊啲咩有冇分寸呀大佬<br />\n<br />\n其實睇返佢嘅FB Page 都叫做有上水有做下野嘅 但個態度同埋自我中心就真係要改下<br />\n<br />\n素人係要啲時間適應 但其他素人都係到做緊形象工程 你係到破壞緊自己嘅形象 貽笑大方呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳梓維會打得贏葉傲冬 因為葉傲冬係一舊好撚臭嘅大屎 而陳梓維係一舊冇咁臭嘅細屎<br />\n<br />\nlink to 有線新聞刺針訪問<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/153300521509664/posts/1428214584018245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F153300521509664%2Fposts%2F1428214584018245%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDlSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=d473b162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/153300521509664/posts/1428214584018245/</a>"},{"pid":"6c0979315133044799c6a27450de6090e2010786","tid":1810771,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉"},{"pid":"301be44f5b0a5c419c13c4cacc819f39701aed3c","tid":1810771,"uid":129138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"咩區議員有嘢做架咩"},{"pid":"db21ef28ac15f82706cef4aca99a0d55cf78c681","tid":1810771,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n拉及block"},{"pid":"097a9031fbfeb919949ebe4a5a228a2264e9d041","tid":1810771,"uid":223256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n作為抗爭者<br />\n跟本就唔應該要求d 所謂當選既手足去做區議員本份<br />\n<br />\n佢地係代表民意去繼續抗爭<br />\n而唔係做區佬呀你老母臭化<br />\n<br />\n陳梓維、我唔會叫你做議員<br />\n只會當你係手足<br />\n<br />\n我想你呢四年做既野<br />\n唔係做區議員<br />\n而係做返六個月做過既野<br />\n果三皮幾人工<br />\n唔該你每個月捐一皮比手足<br />\n<br />\n咪撚去開會<br />\n否則手足會幫你裝修"},{"pid":"2c37cb458c8b3863d7de4499a9ad0341da1c9e23","tid":1810771,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097a9031fbfeb919949ebe4a5a228a2264e9d041","tid":1810771,"uid":223256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n作為抗爭者<br />\n跟本就唔應該要求d 所謂當選既手足去做區議員本份<br />\n<br />\n佢地係代表民意去繼續抗爭<br />\n而唔係做區佬呀你老母臭化<br />\n<br />\n陳梓維、我唔會叫你做議員<br />\n只會當你係手足<br />\n<br />\n我想你呢四年做既野<br />\n唔係做區議員<br />\n而係做返六個月做過既野<br />\n果三皮幾人工<br />\n唔該你每個月捐一皮比手足<br />\n<br />\n咪撚去開會<br />\n否則手足會幫你裝修"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"一睇就知你係 mon post 狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6dc8a741b2dc0ad04ccb6d6e522a72277dc9b2","tid":1810771,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}